                                                  "name": "Body",
                                                  "fill": "$foreground",
                                                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                                                  "width": "fill_container",
                                                  "content": "When you hold the voice button, audio is captured and sent to our speech provider to produce a transcript. We retain the transcript to populate your task; the raw audio clip is kept for 30 days so you can replay or re-transcribe it, then automatically deleted. You can delete any clip immediately from the recording's overflow menu.",
