                                          "name": "P",
                                          "fill": "$foreground",
                                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                                          "width": "fill_container",
                                          "content": "We collect crash reports and basic, non-identifying usage events (for example, “timeline opened”) to keep the app stable. Diagnostics never include the text of your tasks or the content of recordings.",
